Name: Verify Installed apps details info via UI
Description:
### Pre-conditions:
- Shell app installed.

### Steps:
- Login with valid credentials.
- Click `Installed Apps` button.
- Click `Details` button on installed app container.

### Verify that:

- Shell app Details info is valid.

Name: Verify Installed apps details info via API
Description:
### Pre-conditions:
- Shell app installed.

### Steps:
- Login with valid credentials.
- Call `instances` API.

### Verify that:

- API response contains valid data.

Name: Verify User can reach Shell app Details page from Installed Apps page
Description:
### Pre-conditions:
- Shell app installed.

### Steps:
- Login with valid credentials.
- Click Installed Apps.
- Click `Details` button on installed app container.

### Verify that:

- `Shell app Details` page displayed.

Name: Verify installed Shell app listed in Installed apps via UI
Description:
### Pre-conditions:
- Shell app installed.

### Steps:
- Login with valid credentials.
- Click Installed Apps.

### Verify that:

- Shell app displayed in Installed Apps.

Name: Verify User can reach Installed apps page from app container via UI
Description:
### Pre-conditions:
- Shell app installed.

### Steps:
- Login with valid credentials.
- Click `Show All` button on Shell App container.

### Verify that:

- Shell app displayed in Installed Apps.

Name: Install Shell app via UI
Description:
- Login with valid credentials.
- Create new organization via **API**.
- Create new project via **API**.

### Verify that:

- User can install `Shell` app via **UI**.

Name: Verify User can uninstall app via UI
Description:
### Pre-conditions:
- Shell app installed.

### Steps:
- Login with valid credentials.
- Click `Installed Apps` button.
- Click `Details` button on installed app container.
- Click `Uninstall` button.

### Verify that:

- Shell app uninstalled.

Name: Verify installed Shell app info displayed on the app container via UI
Description:
### Pre-conditions:
- Shell app installed.

### Steps:
- Login with valid credentials.

### Verify that:

- Label `Installed` is displayed on the Shell app container.
- `Show All` button displayed on the Shell app container.
